<para style="q1">

<verse number="40" style="v" />You gave me the back of my enemies' necks; I annihilated those who hated me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="41" style="v" />They called for help, but no one saved them; they called out to Yahweh, but he did not answer them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="42" style="v" />I beat them into fine pieces like dust before the wind; I threw them out like mud in the streets.</para>
